cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

This paper is about automated evaluation and improvement of conversational dialogue systems, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, such as training an automated judgement model, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential application of the metric in deployed systems and the need for further research, which could fall under cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) respectively.
